  schema:name "Introduction to Double-Entry Bookkeeping" ;
  schema:description "After completing this lesson, you'll be able to record simple business transactions as double-entry [journal entries](../terms/journal.md), explain why every transaction affects at least two [accounts](../terms/account.md), and verify your entries by checking that [debits equal credits](../terms/trial-balance.md)." ;
